5️⃣ Notifications kya hai?
Notification = Email send karne ka mechanism

Notification decide karta hai:-
kisko email bhejna hai
kaunsa template use hoga
kab email bhejna hai

Example:-
Access approval
Password reset
Policy violation

()Notification ke important methods:-
1️⃣ setTo(String email):-
Email kis ko bhejna hai.
notification.setTo("rahul@gmail.com");

3️⃣ setSubject(String subject):-
Email subject set karta hai.
notification.setSubject("Access Approved");

4️⃣ setBody(String body):-
Email ka message set karta hai.
notification.setBody("Your access request approved");

5️⃣ setTemplate(EmailTemplate template):-
Email template attach karta hai.
notification.setTemplate(template);

6️⃣ send():-
Email send karta hai.
notification.send();
Output:-
Email Sent Successfully

